{"tid":337388,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）美機動遊戲拋出多名遊客 1死7傷","createTime":"2017-07-27T09:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T12:36:54.000Z","uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b111369212d075b03b66226930aa097bf957c051","tid":337388,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州一個嘉年華會有機動遊戲發生致命意外，造成至少1人死亡7人受傷，其中5名傷者危殆。<br />\n<br />\n事發在俄亥俄州立嘉年華（Ohio State Fair），機動遊戲「火球」（Fireball）周三晚故障，有目擊者剛好拍攝到出事一刻，片段可見多名遊客突然被拋至半空，直墮地上。當局指一人當場死亡，傷者中5人受傷勢嚴重，情況危殆，其餘兩人情況穩定。<br />\n嘉年華原本預計會舉辦至下月6日，事發後州長下令展開全面調查，所有嘉年華中的機動遊戲要關閉，直至完成安全檢查為止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170727/57007117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170727%2F57007117&d=ELUN%2FiwwjC2LvQyS5Q5eCGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=bacf2603\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170727%2F57007117&h=61d36d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170727/57007117</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef21ed888b5abce209d2d19a673e00e2624666b","tid":337388,"uid":27017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"又係強國"},{"pid":"e2125137dfaa63f3c10fd4278f8256430b641722","tid":337388,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84d153796360913cfde9e78ccc3f800818552a7a","tid":337388,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"強國<i